@page "/"


<div class="card">
    <h1 class="card-header">Data Binding Examples</h1>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p class="card-text">
            This is a working example of various binding techniques for Blazor.
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
            Please use the menu to work through the different options - if you work down the list, I think you will see how we have to accomodate the fact there are some <i>issues</i> in data-binding in Blazor.
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
            The code is on GitHub <a href="https://github.com/SQL-MisterMagoo/BlazorBinding">Blazor Binding Source</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h5 class="card-header">Changelog</h5>
    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card">
            <h6 class="card-header">9th December 2018</h6>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Migrate to dotnetcore 3.0.100-preview-009812 and Razor Components / Blazor 0.8.0-preview1-20181122.3</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h6 class="card-header">6th December 2018</h6>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Add page showing the problem with click propagation</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h6 class="card-header">5th December 2018</h6>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Style update from <a href="https://github.com/conficient">Howard Richards</a>, including the ColorCode reference.</p>
                <p class="card-text">The syntax highlighting is implemented using <a href="https://github.com/WilliamABradley/ColorCode-Universal">ColorCode</a></p>
                <div class="form-group callout-child">
                    <DisplayCode Code="@(new[] {
                "<DisplayCode Code=\"@(new[] {\"<input id=\"parent\" type=\"checkbox\" bind=\"@ParentValue\" />\"})\" />",
                })" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h6 class="card-header">5th December 2018</h6>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Now using a new DisplayCode component that is simpler and highlights syntax</p>
                <p class="card-text">The syntax highlighting was implemented using <a href="https://github.com/SQL-MisterMagoo/highlight">my dotnetstandard fork</a> of the project <a href="https://github.com/thomasjo/highlight">highlight by thomasjo</a></p>
                <div class="form-group callout-child">
                    <DisplayCode Code="@(new[] {
                        "<DisplayCode Code=\"@(new[]{",
                            "   \"<CascadingValue Name=\"ParentValue\" Value=\"@ParentValue\">\",",
                            "   \" <CheckBox />\",",
                            "   \"</CascadingValue>\",",
                            "    })\"/>",
                    })" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h6 class="card-header">27th November 2018</h6>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">Style update from <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/edcharbeneau">Ed Charbeneau</a>, including these cards</p>
                <div class="form-group callout-child">
                    Watch Ed's show #StateHasChanged on Twitch
                    <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/edcharbeneau">#StateHasChanged</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
